Contributing

Contributions are welcome! To submit a contribution, please open a pull
request or contact the author via https://github.com/radiospiel.

Copyright Waiver

By submitting a contribution you waive all copyright and related rights to
your contribution, transferring them to the original author. This allows the
project to be relicensed or redistributed without requiring permission from
individual contributors.

If you are not willing or able to waive copyright, please discuss this with
the author before submitting.
